Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「關於香港的新聞 由於情報不…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了… 小要?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恭子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生體不舒服嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我帶你去保健室?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年4班的 千鳥要同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:02:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請到教師辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像是相良同學寄到事務室來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你別太激動聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥同學…你沒事麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 比起這個 裡面是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…退學書…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他最近確實總是請假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是連商量都沒有 就突然寄來退學書…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道該怎麼辦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說呢 千鳥同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是怎麼回事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是又吵架了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天還沒不能聯繫上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就得把這個交給校長處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是說是退學了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 那個傢伙已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是有人盯上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是不能回來救你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被監視是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想對策才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能把老師和恭子他們牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要振作一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是一個只會在塔上歎氣的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是情報 必須弄清我身邊發生的事情!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是我多心了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「竊聽 偷拍 專用人員為你解除不安!」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是一個人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吃好吃的吧 我來請客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼酒呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是知道有個氣氛不錯的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 我現在很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 想和我去旅館嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 快點進去吧 水樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面雨很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了水樹 大叔我會很用功的哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備選那個房間?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,202房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 還有更好的房間嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個看起來很狹小的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 開玩笑的 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那間好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水樹～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡等下再說 也沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦 水樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 是女高中生的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下 到底誰是被害者呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說…這個應該沒問題吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡的話 周圍的情況都可以看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人的話…就一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動 我正用武器瞄準你!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起雙手 轉過來!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來注意到發信器了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是找我有事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就專程過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…所以才和陌生男人到那種旅館…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是有些輕視你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 你帶搶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢拿出來 扔到腳下!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Mithril的人 是不會對你不利的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不相信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別得意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不能殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還可以封住你那囂張的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 更糟糕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近幾天 除了我以外還有其他人在跟蹤…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你把搶放下 混蛋!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 千鳥要 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打中嗎? 會起作用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是圈套吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被發現了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼圈套嗎?會被殺掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是向她求饒才好??!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是專家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能贏他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到這種事情時就不應該心軟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把獵物放在眼前玩弄是三流的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是你贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 認為這世界上有兩種女性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適合雨景的 和 不適合的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你絕對是前者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到現在的你 誰都會這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在諷刺我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最高級的讚美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你是同類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我是來救你的」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…雖然想這麼說 但其實也不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐視不理 也可以來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 結果可能也不會有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人不爽的口氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話不能直接一些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事情說的太清楚 是會有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可能 這才是你的魅力所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是泰莎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來吧 玉蘭 應該已經醒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sliver 你有在看?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是你應該應對的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於無視組織一事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以替你辯護求情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能說服在香港暴走的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我們會服從嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇什麼的 是件非常空虛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是老師的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我還活著 就會取那女人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就永別了 玉蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的人是你 雷納德·泰斯特羅莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下達指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以A-1處理 給我徹底的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-1處理 結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指定的威脅已完全沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 待機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃案1211 Alastor(死刑執行者)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是世界最小的AS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在的你應該是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AS的自律行動很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動力源和控制系統的微型化也花了我不少精力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是我這次真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看了些煞風景的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不..不明白緣故 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用殺了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈求這種結果的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是是她本人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還沒你的「男朋友」殺的人多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…他從小就一直在戰爭中…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身不由己的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也儘是些壞人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也會救助無辜者或比自己弱的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 他絕對沒有享受這類事情!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…他…和你是不一樣的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不會這樣子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是真的相信這種歪理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方的行為本質都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你 只責怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺會幫著他的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜歡他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看著我這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 待機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是 讓睡美人清醒之吻 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我討厭你 噁心死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡上你這點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即虛幻又兇猛 看似粗野卻又高貴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人捉摸不定的 似水的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你還沒想殺我之前 我先撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來是 有事找他的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有理由 要聽你的話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原諒你對我所做的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把他給放下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開之前我再說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心喜歡上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 以後再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你動不了嗎? 受傷了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被剛才那男的 注射了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我救你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我也是有自尊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種失敗…這樣的失態…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…還不如這樣死了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…你不在這裡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你不在…才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我…不要這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…待在我身邊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我說「沒問題」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛有說過「不如死了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多抵抗幾下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也一直會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}きっと君は今日の日も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}你今天一定也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}真っ直ぐ明日を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}直視著明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}風が吹くあの丘に咲いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}彷彿在那微風吹過的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}向日葵のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}綻放的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}どんなに遠く離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}即使相離再遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}この歌声が君に届くように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}也要把這歌聲傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}涙がずっと止まらない夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}在這滿臉淚痕的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}君の窓を照らす月になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}希望成為照亮你窗前的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}また必ず会えると そう思うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}一定會再相見的 我這麼相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何而戰…?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萎縮的心和漸失的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對新的任務 我什麼都看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「兩個香港」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而後 舞台即將轉移到混亂的城市
